":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:33:26.000Z","msg":"其實呢D野唔同人睇唔同, 你問我最惡頂係懲教. 要入去陪坐監.<br />\n救護就最忙, 警察忙加麻煩濕星野多, 咩都要識搞. 消防就要長操同埋一有大鑊野都真係大鑊."},{"pid":"e188fcddeda028d79986cc6eb20a4644dc686896","tid":230187,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:48:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/05/151933_48f65ec53e04880aeb3cffc5c9315138.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F05%2F151933_48f65ec53e04880aeb3cffc5c9315138.jpg&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjBFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=ad8520ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/05/151933_48f65ec53e04880aeb3cffc5c9315138.jpg</a>&quot;  /&gt;<br />\n笑而不語</blockquote><br />\n試下消防冇頭盔會點<br />\n有裝備同冇裝備比<br />\non9</blockquote><br />\n辛苦你，又要做假膠提升討論氣氛</blockquote><br />\n有point就駁<br />\n駁唔到就遊花園"},{"pid":"09e3e5a925cf37205f5d272903fd941f8dcf1a68","tid":230187,"uid":2613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:06:44.000Z","msg":"班消防要求加人工啫，又唔係要班警察減人工。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋衝出嚟做乜柒？"},{"pid":"0e540a887b659d2eb7cc55c1fa57e75076a2ffa4","tid":230187,"uid":71462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:08:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班消防要求加人工啫，又唔係要班警察減人工。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋衝出嚟做乜柒？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n班警犬唔抵得 又想加"},{"pid":"1cf1f28684deb8f94a61992fba2c7dddcae7fd20","tid":230187,"uid":30487,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:40:33.000Z","msg":"警犬叫雞唔洗錢又唔講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2601376a8aa998aadc8051eab11e8451232753f","tid":230187,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T00:28:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警犬叫雞唔洗錢又唔講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n福利好幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=